comments: Grant (DET) legally contests Mann's (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Plumlee (DET) and Zubac (LAC) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Mann (LAC) is moving alongside Hayes' (DET) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Zubac (LAC) places a hand on Grant (DET) and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Plumlee (DET) and Mann (LAC) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs during rebounding.
Plumlee (DET) brushes Jackson's (LAC) arm as he is securing the loose ball, and contact is marginal.
Zubac (LAC) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Grant (DET) legally contests Zubac's (LAC) shot near the rim.
Hayes (DET) makes contact with the ball as he defends Zubac's (LAC) shot near the rim.
Batum (LAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Plumlee (DET).
Coffey (LAC) moves forward into Plumlee's (DET) body and delivers contact as he defends the shot near the rim.
Grant (DET) legally contests Mann's (LAC) shot near the rim.
Batum (LAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Grant (DET).
Hayes (DET) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Mann's (LAC) drive.
Bey (DET) cleanly deflects the ball away from Coffey (LAC).  Any ensuing body contact is incidental.
Plumlee (DET) is bracing for the contact from Mann (LAC) and releases away from the contact.
Coffey (LAC) legally contests Hayes' (DET) jump shot attempt.
